Idea: The Worlds Aplenty's version of a multiverse. Decanoluzioned Fictions exists as endless alternate versions of The Infinite Fields layered atop it. Rather than typical multiverse concepts, since The Worlds Aplenty's sky is already made of timelines, "multiversal variants" of characters not from/within timelines are impossible. Rather, "multiversal variants" of Infinite Field characters exist as "Decanoluzioned Variants". The concept is similar, with the sole exception that all Decanoluzioned Variants do not exist.
Some technologies are capable of tapping into this plane, however, such as the Alternate Fiction.

The term is a combination of "Decanonized" and "Delusion", or perhaps even "Illusion" instead.